{
  "title": "ISic003550. An antiquarian 'forgery'",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Πετρονία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Πετρονία\">Πετρονία</span></span> [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">. 7.</span>] <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ἔζησεν ἀμέμπτως καὶ σεμνῶς <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ἔτη <span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ιβ</span>´ μῆνας <span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">δ</span>´ ἱμέρας <span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">δ</span>´ <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γάϊος · Κορνήλιος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Γάϊος\">Γ(άϊος)</span> · <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Κορνήλιος\">Κορνήλιος</span></span> πατὴρ <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>εἰδίᾳ εἰδίᾳ [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">. 5.</span>] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Πετρονία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Πετρονία\">ΠΕΤΡΟΝΙΑ</span></span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·······</span>]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΕΖΗΣΕΝΑΜΕΜΠΤΩΣΚΑΙΣΕΜΝΩΣ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΕΤΗ<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">ΙΒ</span>ΜΗΝΑΣ<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Δ</span>ΙΜΕΡΑΣ<span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\">Δ</span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γάϊος · Κορνήλιος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Γάϊος\">Γ</span>·<span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Κορνήλιος\">ΚΟΡΝΗΛΙΟΣ</span></span>ΠΑΤΗΡ<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>ΕΙΔΙΑΕΙΔΙΑ[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·····</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003550_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003550_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003550.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003550-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text after comparison of Kaibel, Filippi and SEG, prioritising Kaibel's transcription of the manuscript tradition</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>As Korhonen lucidly details, the inscription is one of a series of late 18th century local antiquarian forgeries, constructed on the basis of existing texts, principally those to be found in the 1769 first edition of the corpus of Torremuzza. Kaibel classed the entire series already as forgeries in IG XIV.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 52.0895 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">17*</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a></li><li> Filippi 2002 74 no. 1/9 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001991\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001991</a></li><li> Filippi 2005 63 no. 1/9 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002296\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002296</a></li><li> Korhonen 2017 198 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001484\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001484</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
